metadata.name: JD Orange
metadata.description:
This original sketch created as the foundation for its 48x36" oil painting. This digital drawing was made in Photoshop, and is in its original dimensions of 2100x2100. Signed by D'Vincent as part of the Emerging series.

The original photograph was taken by Dax Smith, as a part of his series paying homage to other famous artists. This series of photos was designed to represent the style of Caravaggio.
